data.description: ****Seller has an assumable VA loan with a 2.25% interest rate****Quiet top floor condo, with fantastic mountain views, near open space, courtyard facing, an open floorplan, low HOA that includes heat, close carport parking, and wood burning fireplace that is not to be missed! This condo features thoughtful upgrades, new flooring, all in one washer hookups along with community provided machines next door, and an incredible central location.  It is near Belmar shopping, grocery stores, easy highway access, and around 15 minutes to Downtown Denver while being central to the mountains and Red Rocks. Seller is open to selling fully furnished or selling individual items of furniture if it will benefit an interested buyer. The HOA fees are low and the community features storage, onsite laundry (there are hookups in the unit), a clubhouse for gatherings, and an inviting outdoor pool. This is a beautiful and peaceful place with all the features you have been searching for, so come take a look and make this condo your new home!
